{
  "title": "Rich Mediterranean Collards Stir-fry",
  "description": "A rich and velvety mediterranean dish featuring collards with a gluten-free twist that is sure to be a crowd-pleaser.",
  "cuisine": "Mediterranean",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free"
